Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.42,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}仿佛在欺骗我一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.01,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.59,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}交替变换
