Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.77,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}越想越觉得可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:36.41,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}明明自己一动不动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.55,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}如此可笑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.95,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}怎能沉默不语
