Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.31,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}Been  thinking  about  you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.49,0:30:38.81,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}And  there's  no  rest
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.81,0:30:40.93,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}Should  I  still  love  you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:43.05,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}Still  see  you  in  bed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.32,0:30:45.62,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}But  I'm  playing  with  myself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:48.07,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}What  do  you  care
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:51.48,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}When  the  other  men  are  far  far  better
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:54.99,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}All  the  things  you've  got
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.40,0:30:57.49,Lyrics-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}All  the  things  you  need
