Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.71,0:30:17.87,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}我一直在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:20.30,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你的唱片在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.50,0:30:22.43,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你总是看向我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:24.61,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你的笑容却朝向那里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.87,0:30:27.25,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}可我还是默默无闻
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.43,0:30:29.21,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}而你就是我的明星
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.51,0:30:31.93,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你会在乎什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.31,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}我一直在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.49,0:30:38.81,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}从不停息
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.81,0:30:40.93,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}我是否该继续爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:43.05,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}看你仍卧于床榻
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.32,0:30:45.62,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}可我却在独自消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:48.07,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你会在乎什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:51.48,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}当别的男人都远胜于我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:54.99,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你拥有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.40,0:30:57.49,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}你需要的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.49,0:30:59.41,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}谁为你买了香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:06.12,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3a&80&}谁又会想方设法地去见你
